{{Infobox person |honorific_prefix = |name = Livienne Russellia |honorific_suffix = |native_name = |native_name_lang = |image = |image_size = |alt = |caption = |birth_name = Livienne Russellia |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1976|3|4}} |birth_place = [[Pontianak]], [[West Kalimantan]] |disappeared_date = |disappeared_place = |disappeared_status = |death_date = |death_place = |death_cause = |body_discovered = |resting_place = |resting_place_coordinates = |monuments = |residence = |nationality = {{flag|Indonesia}} |other_names = |ethnicity = |citizenship = |education = |alma_mater = [[Tarumanagara University]] |occupation = Businesswoman |years_active = |employer = |organization = |agent = |known_for = |notable_works = |style = |influences = |influenced = |home_town = |salary = |net_worth = |height = |weight = |title = |term = |predecessor = |successor = |movement = |opponents = |boards = |religion = |denomination = |criminal_charge = |criminal_penalty = |criminal_status = |spouse = |partner = |children = |parents = |relatives = |callsign = |awards = |signature = |signature_alt = |signature_size = |module = |module2 = |module3 = |module4 = |module5 = |module6 = |twitter = |website = {{URL|www.cakradaya.com}} |footnotes = |box_width = }}
'''Livienne Russellia''' (born in [[Pontianak]], March 4, 1976) is a businesswoman, sosialite, and beauty expert in [[Indonesia]].<ref name="beritasatu">{{cite web|url=http://www.beritasatu.com/investor/467910-livienne-russellia-berpikir-positif-di-saat-sulit.html|title=Livienne Russellia, Berpikir Positif di Saat Sulit|website=BeritaSatu.com|accessdate=2018-07-15}}</ref><ref name="tempo">{{cite web|url=https://gaya.tempo.co/read/871198/hari-buruh-pengusaha-ini-kedepankan-hubungan-humanis|author=Hadriani Pudjiarti|title=Hari Buruh, Pengusaha Ini Kedepankan Hubungan Humanis! - Gaya Tempo.co|website=gaya.tempo.co|accessdate=2018-07-15}}</ref> She holds a graduate degree in cosmetic pharmacy from [[Universitas Pancasila]],
Livienne not only active in business and beauty industry but also in other organization such as PPA Kosmetika Indonesia and Lions Club. In 2017 she was awarded Top 10 Influenced Women Award by Asosiasi Duta Indonesia (ADI).<ref name="beritasatu2">{{cite web|url=http://www.beritasatu.com/gayahidup-keluarga/423707-adi-serahkan-penghargaan-untuk-10-wanita-panutan-2017.html|title=ADI Serahkan Penghargaan untuk 10 Wanita Panutan 2017|website=BeritaSatu.com|accessdate=2018-07-15}}</ref> earlier in 2015 she also received the MNC Lifestyle award <ref name="possore">{{cite web|url=https://possore.com/2015/12/18/agnes-dan-maudy-rebut-penghargaan-mnc/|title=Agnes dan Maudy Rebut Penghargaan MNC Lifestyle 2015|website=Pos Sore|accessdate=2018-07-15}}</ref>
== Career == Livienne Russellia is listed as the commissioner of PT. Cakra Daya Makmur which operate in beauty industry.<ref name="swa">{{cite web|url=https://swa.co.id/swa/trends/marketing/pengusaha-cantik-ini-semakin-percaya-diri-garap-pasar-kosmetika|title=Pengusaha Cantik Ini Semakin Percaya Diri Garap Pasar Kosmetika|website=SWA.co.id|accessdate=2018-07-15}}</ref>
